    Specifies the location of a point relative to a rectangle. Immutable class containing a pair of LineLocation values indicating the location of each point dimension relative to the corresponding rectangle edge. For this purpose, the rectangle edges are interpreted as directed line segments starting at the minimum coordinate and ending at the maximum coordinate.
